in addition, sheriff's jail and transportation officers have been hired for the week, and 10 agents from the state alcoholic beverage control board will be on the lookout for liquor sales to minors, officials said
during the 1986 spring break, hundreds of vacationing youths went on a good friday rampage, hurling bottles at police, tearing clothes off young women and briefly taking over the main street of town
to prevent a recurrence last year, palm springs distributed 45,000 pamphlets to local schools and colleges warning that visitors were expected to obey the law. a strengthened police force awaited vacationers, including 40 officers from the riverside county sheriff's department and the california highway patrol
